but when i use PhantomJS shot a webpage,it is normal, more details as follow:
first: i want to scrap a webpage : http://www.huya.com/weigege ,this is my code
@config(age=102460*60, priority=2)

def list_page(self, response):
for each in response.doc('a.video-info').items():
if re.match("http://www.huya.com/\w+", each.attr.href, re.U):
self.crawl(each.attr.href,fetch_type='js',force_update=True,callback=self.detail_page)

when i run my source code , it returns me something like this:
